OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FDry with
OL,6,Fsome evening sunshine to start with,
OL,7,Fleading to lengthy clear spells
OL,8,Fovernight.
OL,9,
OL,10,CSaturday:FIt will be another dry day
OL,11,Fwith plenty of sunshine though a bit
OL,12,Fmore cloud than previous days. Warm
OL,13,Fagain in the west, but a bit cooler
OL,14,Faround Greater Glasgow.
OL,15,
OL,16,COutlook for Sunday to Tuesday:FBright
OL,17,Fspells and variable cloud on Sunday
OL,18,Fand Monday with the chance of a few
OL,19,Fshowers. Dry with sunny spells again
OL,20,FTuesday, warmer in the west.
